USB_ROOT
├── disk_cleanup.bat            (Main batch script for disk cleanup and sequence start)
├── show_image.ps1              (PowerShell script for displaying an image fullscreen)
├── barbie_pink.ps1             (PowerShell script for pink screen and beep)
├── hide_taskbar_desktop.ahk    (AutoHotkey script for hiding UI elements)
├── assets/
│   ├── pink_skull.jpg          (Image to display in fullscreen)
│   ├── alert_sound.wav         (Optional: Custom sound file for beep)
└── IrfanView.exe               (Portable IrfanView, optional if needed)
